CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 21, 1951, pg. 9 reads: " Achievement Club Group 8 - The climax of a successful self-denial drive of Achievement Club Group 8 was a lovely dinner at the Loendi Club, Sunday, July 1. Members and guests included Mmes. Belle Hodson, Lillian Howard, Velma Combs, Mary Clark, Remedios Thompson, Bertha Brandon, Lucy Wigfall, Ernestine Wade, Virginia Wright, Hazel Patterson, Etta Forst, Nellie Tanner, Mamie Williams, Myrtle Johnson, Ernestine Carter, Lillian Aughtry, Sophronia Collington, and George Lee, E. L. Johnson and Roosevelt Daniels.  Mary Clark is president."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Achievement Club Group 8 members and guests, including Belle Hodson, Lillian Howard, Velma Combs, Mary Clark, Remedios Thompson, Bertha Brandon, Lucy Wigfall, Ernestine Wade, Virginia Wright, Hazel Patterson, Etta Forst, Nellie Tanner, Mamie Williams, Myrtle Johnson, Ernestine Carter, Lillian Aughtry, Sophronia Collington, George Lee, E. L. Johnson and Roosevelt Daniels, gathered in Loendi Club for dinner
